description: Johnny stopped over Ryan's house the other day and ended up staying the weekend. These two had been friends since they graduated from high school, last year. Johnny was in the guest bedroom playing with his phone when Ryan walked in and offered to help him make his phone work better. After Ryan fixed it, he told Johnny that he needed to be compensated for his work. Johnny had no money on him and was confused. Ryan, however, was thinking about sex and since Johnny was kinda curious, he decided to give it a whirl. It is a safe assumption that, after this hot fuck session, Johnny is a big ole bottom boy now!
title: Take It From The Top
